Checkpoint 4 - Wild Circus - User Stories

As the administrator, I can create, edit, and delete :
- performers
- acts
- events

As a visitor, I can view :
- performers
- acts (and the associated performers)
- events (and the associated acts)

As a visitor, I can :
- contact the site administrator
- book tickets to an event

Bonus :
Spectators can use a QR code to gain access to the event they booked (e-ticket)
